content: Gorgeous deck!
My favorite tarot app.
Lisa Hunt is a phenomenal artist! This deck is hauntingly beautiful and I love it and this application!
Love this deck!
Absolutely beautiful deck I'm intrigued by the spirit world etc so I'm very much in love with this deck so far
very nice.

Great little app - have it so I can carry easily the cards with me - as I 
have the deck too.

Love the app, but the card meanings are very brief.  It allows for reverse cards, but no reverse card meanings.  Trust me, the reverse of some of the card meanings is not necessarily easy to determine.
Beautiful art work. Love the background story on each card
Well done! Beautiful tarot deck. The app works perfectly on both, my tablet and my phone.
I love this app. I also have this deck which i have trimmed. The deck for me is direct and straight to the point and for me easy to read.

Beautiful Artwork , Descriptions , Spreads .  The App Actually Speaks to you as well As the Actual Deck itself. I use Both Every day . As A Tarot reader , I have Used the Card of the day with a Card of the day I have pulled from My Deck . Many times it tells a Message , and many times I've pulled the same card as the card of the day on this App.  Both are wonderful and compliment each other well .. Love it
Surprised by how beautiful the art is and how much I love it!!
I haven't really got to see how they work
Wonderful app, with great features. Works flawlessly. The art is beautiful, and descriptions are educational and interesting. Im interested in buying the physical deck now.
I love it, just need overallexplanation of cards at the end of reading
Haunting,  beautiful cards! Intriguing deck. Love the stories and legends and how well they describe the card's meaning.
Great  for reading

The artwork has so much feeling it's incredible. The interface is very intuitive. I just think of something I want to do and I can do it. You can write comments on particular cards or on the reading in general. I can't imagine a way to make it better.
Love it

The interface is beautifully designed and allows interactivity with the companion volume. The many spreads available, the journal, and the personalized cloth are wonderful touches, as well as the card of the day. The artwork of the deck itself is fantastic.
Very cool
Beautiful app.
